---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CTA from '../components/CTA.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.jsx';
---

<Layout title="Quick2query - Our Journey">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <HeroSection 
      title="Our"
      highlight="Story"
      subtitle="Born from a student project to revolutionize how businesses interact with their data. We're making enterprise data accessible to everyone, no technical skills required."
      client:load
    />

    <!-- Story Content -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-text font-primary">Turning a Challenge into Innovation</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-secondary">
              What started as a group of students tackling a real-world problem has evolved into a mission to democratize data access for businesses worldwide.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text font-primary">The Challenge We Discovered</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 font-secondary">
                During our work with ERP companies, we identified a fundamental issue affecting their clients: 
                business users couldn't independently query and analyze the centralized information in their systems.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-secondary">
                This technical barrier was creating bottlenecks, delaying decisions, and limiting the value companies 
                could extract from their own data. We knew there had to be a better way.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-background/30 border-2 border-tech/20 rounded-xl p-8">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-tech rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-tech font-medium">Business users dependent on IT teams</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-tech rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-tech font-medium">Hours or days waiting for data insights</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-tech rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-tech font-medium">Limited data exploration capabilities</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-tech rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-tech font-medium">Missed opportunities for data-driven decisions</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
            <div class="bg-primary/10 border-2 border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-8">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-primary font-medium">Natural Language Processing</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-primary font-medium">Instant Query Generation</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-primary font-medium">Universal Database Support</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                  <span class="text-primary font-medium">No Technical Skills Required</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text font-primary">Our Solution</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 font-secondary">
                This challenge validated an enormous market opportunity. We combined our expertise in AI and 
                our understanding of enterprise needs to create a transformative tool for businesses of all sizes.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 font-secondary">
                Quick2Query bridges the gap between business questions and data answers, enabling anyone to 
                explore company information simply by asking.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-neutral rounded-xl p-8 mb-16">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-text font-primary text-center">What Quick2Query Means</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2 font-primary">"Quick"</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 font-secondary">
                  Reflects our commitment to immediacy, get answers instantly, eliminating waits and technical dependencies.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-tech mb-2 font-primary">"2"</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 font-secondary">
                  Symbolizes the direct, bidirectional dialogue we create between users and their data. 
                  It also suggests the ability to combine with any action, representing speed in everything you do.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-text font-primary">Our First Product</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 font-secondary">
              Quick2Query is the materialization of our vision: a solution designed so anyone can explore 
              and understand their company's information simply by asking questions in natural language.
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
              <div class="bg-primary/10 border-2 border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-6">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-2 font-primary">Instant</div>
                <div class="text-primary font-medium font-secondary">Get Answers in Seconds</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-tech/10 border-2 border-tech/20 rounded-xl p-6">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-tech mb-2 font-primary">Any Database</div>
                <div class="text-tech font-medium font-secondary">ERP, CRM, Custom Systems</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-accent/10 border-2 border-accent/20 rounded-xl p-6">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-2 font-primary">Zero Code</div>
                <div class="text-accent font-medium font-secondary">No Technical Skills Needed</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-tech/5 to-primary/5 rounded-xl p-8 text-center border-2 border-tech/20">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-text font-primary">Our Mission</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-secondary">
              To empower every business professional with instant access to their data, eliminating technical 
              barriers and enabling faster, smarter decisions. We're building the future where asking a question 
              is all it takes to unlock insights.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <CTA />
  <Footer />
</Layout>